latestIgtvVideos.title: Summer Bronze Glow
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey Guys! Here’s presenting you my all time Favourite Warm Matte Eyes 👀 I hope you like it. For product details just ask in the comment section below 👇🏻
.
.

Tip of the Day : Always apply a generous coat of mascara on the lower lashes. It completely changes the look and defines the eye. Never go without it. It’s my Holygrail 🙌🏻
